com.palomamobile.android.sdk.message

Interface IMessageService


  • public interface IMessageService
    This interface is consumed by the Retrofit library to provide access to the Paloma Mobile Platform Sharing and Messaging Service RESTful API. All calls are synchronous. To get a concrete implementation of this interface call IServiceManager.getService() This class provides somewhat low level access to the Server API it may be more convenient to use methods in IMessageManager.
    See Also:
    Paloma Mobile Platform Sharing and Messaging Service RESTful API
